{
  "texts": [
    "The mid-tier version called Gemini Pro is found to perform in between GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 on a number of LLM evaluation benchmarks (Gemini Team, 2023).",
    "13 Our results in Table 5 confirm this finding showing high performance of Gemini Pro closer to GPT-4 than GPT-3.5.",
    "The large context window of Gemini Pro, which spans 32k tokens, significantly more than the 4k token limit of GPT-3.5-0301, enables the inclusion of the 300 training sentences directly within the prompt history, acting as a \"few shot\" learner.",
    "This approach further boosts performance, making Gemini almost perform on GPT-4 levels.",
    "The fact that fine-tuned GPT-3.5, GPT-4 and Gemini can outperform 3.5 on a prompt that was engineered using GPT 3.5 is further evidence that model characteristics play a larger role than prompt engineering can."
  ]
}